; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the date fallback path in lot matching.  When lots are created
; without explicit date annotations (no [date] in {price}), the code
; falls back to finding the earliest transaction date for that lot
; from the account's prior postings.

2024/01/01 Buy Lot 1
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Buy Lot 2
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$160.00}
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/01 Sell
    Assets:Brokerage    -7 AAPL @ $170.00
    Assets:Cash

test --lot-matching fifo reg Assets:Brokerage
24-Jan-01 Buy Lot 1             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL       5 AAPL
24-Feb-01 Buy Lot 2             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL      10 AAPL
24-Mar-01 Sell                  Assets:Brokerage            -5 AAPL       5 AAPL
                                Assets:Brokerage            -2 AAPL       3 AAPL
end test
